      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 1.627146,
      "replayEndSec": 7.928955,
      "narrationText": "首先，让我们创建一个配置文件。该文件将保存 SSH 密钥、机器列表以及后续所有操作的基础设施配置。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-01.c1bda4ae.mp3",
      "textHash": "c1bda4aed4f1dd42dc11339050b98d3f42bcb4dba64556f01d9216521f1028c7",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.075918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-01-after.a17a9fb3.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.485714,
      "afterTextHash": "a17a9fb3024d64aa345761b6c9bbcdca144b818d035a8adada0d99986d1e6b74"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-add-server-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 7.928955,
      "replayEndSec": 16.338306,
      "narrationText": "现在让我们从命令行注册服务器，提供其名称、IP 地址和 SSH 用户名。主机密钥会自动扫描以建立信任连接。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-02.1238384e.mp3",
      "textHash": "1238384e76f50cdc3a30794d7ced26dca6e7aa0753ea5cd7e5f2048498d49390",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.199184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-02-after.544c6899.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.160816,
      "afterTextHash": "544c6899201bf194d9baa36c260c4e922253c7cda976a5ec64425d45242c6966"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-add-server-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 16.338306,
      "replayEndSec": 18.998199,
      "narrationText": "接下来让我们配置服务器。这一步会安装 renet 并创建加密数据存储。完成后，服务器就可以托管仓库了。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-03.b446fb50.mp3",
      "textHash": "b446fb50e1768f87fd9364123d464bd8638111f983306601aee56c155fa6665d",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.090612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/tutorial-add-server-03-after.5a4a121b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.787755,
      "afterTextHash": "5a4a121b52272084c2a110e925d78ce8549e0b7617ebda24d1fce2afb6f515d5"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "752e51ba1d78cb456e46b40c58eb6dd297873e1758db5f036996bcf81eba78a9",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/intro.752e51ba.mp3",
      "narrationText": "好！我们来添加你的第一台服务器。两条命令，大约一分钟就能搞定。",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.426122
    },
    {
      "id": "two-tool-architecture",
      "textHash": "e8f841c8a866c6d424d50b20598075da231553b79e6b1968fc9ecc74f304f51a",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-add-server/two-tool-architecture.e8f841c8.mp3",
      "narrationText": "整套架构由两部分组成。命令行工具装在你的笔记本上，服务器上则运行一个叫做 renet 的编排器。CLI 通过 SSH 连接服务器，所以你永远不需要手动登录服务器。",
      "audioDurationSec": 18.834286
    },
